{"tid":1631724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非唔該醒醒","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:43.000Z","uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"651d7f70f65940237e32b3e120ba20d1e8bd0d68","tid":1631724,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"而家既遊行唔會有不反對通知書，<br />\n即係對黑警黎講，係屬於一個不合法既活動。<br />\n所以唔好諗住你可以平平安安老馮行完全程，<br />\n亦都唔會好似以前咁，<br />\n俾你去到金鐘先決定離開（向中環方向）定係參戰（向政總方向）。<br />\n只要你出現係現場，就算係行人路都好，<br />\n你都會俾popo拉，受到既對待唔會比勇武好得幾多。<br />\n<br />\n所以真係要時刻保持警覺性，見到唔對路，<br />\n或者塞住好耐既時候，<br />\n請開始退下並衡量有冇決心面對防暴popo，<br />\n冇既話，唔該離開，無謂拖累前線。<br />\n<br />\n利申：資深和理非"},{"pid":"7538cafeb4700e73fc1ef9a2da9096f8f8b10b94","tid":1631724,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n你應承過會做勇武塊盾<br />\n宜家勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿中林鄭割蓆計！</span></strong></span><br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"70aa91f3d5730914f321acbe6ceccfdcd155d398","tid":1631724,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}